ot%3BThe%20officers%20in%20charge%20of%20election%20in%20Telangana%20and%20Sircilla%20are%20not%20Telugu%20people%20and%20they%20hardly%20understand%20the%20local%20dialect%20of%20Telugu.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20criticised%20the%20Congress%20for%20%26quot%3Bpicking%20some%20sentences%20from%20his%20press%20conference%20out%20of%20context.%20The%20English%20translation%20of%20the%20sentences%20is%20not%20correct%20and%20twisted%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKCR%20also%20insisted%20that%20he%20had%20confined%20his%20criticism%20to%20the%20policies%20and%20programmes%20of%20the%20Congress%20and%20that%20he%20made%20no%20criticism%20of%20personal%20aspects%20of%20any%20Congress%20leaders%2C%20the%20Election%20Commission%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20going%20through%20the%20content%20of%20the%20Congress%20complaint%20and%20KCR's%20reply%2C%20the%20commission%20found%20the%20BRS%20chief%20%26quot%3Bhas%20violated%20the%20provisions%20of%20the%20Model%20Code%20of%20Conduct%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EK%20Chandrashekar%20Rao%20is%20the%20second%20politician%20to%20be%20banned%20from%20campaigning%20for%2048%20hours%20after%20Congress%20leader%20Randeep%20Singh%20Surjewala%20in%20the%20ongoing%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714571100000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fbfesojr_k-chandrasekhar-rao_625x300_16_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkcr-barred-from-campaigning-for-derogatory-remarks-against-congress-5565710%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Former%20Telangana%20Chief%20Minister%20and%20Bharat%20Rashtra%20Samithi%20president%20K%20Chandrashekar%20Rao%2C%20popularly%20known%20as%20KCR%2C%20has%20been%20banned%20by%20the%20Election%20Commission%20today%20from%20campaigning%20for%2048%20hours%20for%20his%20%26quot%3Bderogatory%26quot%3B%20statements%20against%20the%20Congress.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkcr-barred-from-campaigning-for-derogatory-remarks-against-congress-5565710%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkcr-barred-from-campaigning-for-derogatory-remarks-against-congress-5565710%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkcr-barred-from-campaigning-for-derogatory-remarks-against-congress-5565710%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22We%20Weren't%20Born%20To%20Commit%20Sin%20Of%20Changing%20Constitution%3A%20PM%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ELaunching%20an%20acerbic%20attack%20on%20the%20Congress%20on%20his%20home%20turf%20of%20Gujarat%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20has%20said%20the%20party%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bfake%20factory%26quot%3B%20and%20accused%20it%20of%20using%20doctored%20videos%20to%20mislead%20the%20people%20during%20the%20ongoing%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20backdrop%20of%20a%20deepfake%20video%20of%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20in%20which%20he%20purportedly%20advocates%20for%20the%20abolition%20of%20reservation%20for%20Scheduled%20Castes%20(SCs)%2C%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20(STs)%2C%20and%20Other%20Backward%20Classes%20(OBCs)%2C%20which%20was%20allegedly%20shared%20by%20some%20Congress%20social%20media%20handles%2C%20PM%20Modi%20claimed%20on%20Wednesday%20that%20the%20party's%20videos%2C%20words%20and%20promises%20are%20all%20fake.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20a%20rally%20in%20Banaskantha%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20said%20in%20Hindi%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20Congress%20has%20opened%20a%20market%20of%20fake%20videos.%20They%20know%20that%20whatever%20they%20are%20saying%20isn't%20working%20in%20the%20elections%20so%20they%20are%20now%20making%20fake%20videos.%20Think%20about%20it%2C%20a%20party%20that%20has%20ruled%20the%20country%20for%2060%20years%2C%20that%20has%20had%20so%20many%20Prime%20Ministers%2C%20can't%20speak%20the%20truth%20to%20people.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaking%20a%20dig%20at%20Congress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20over%20his%20oft-stated%20call%20for%20a%20%26quot%3B%3Cem%3Emohabbat%20ki%20dukaan%3C%2Fem%3E%20(shop%20of%20love)%26quot%3B%20in%20a%20market%20of%20hate%2C%20the%20PM%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BWhat%20they%20used%20to%20call%20a%20'%3Cem%3Emohabbat%20ki%20dukaan%3C%2Fem%3E'%20is%20actually%20a%20fake%20factory.%20Their%20videos%2C%20words%2C%20promises%2C%20slogans%20and%20intentions%20are%20all%20fake.%20Modi%20is%20a%20tea-seller%2C%20the%20son%20of%20poor%20people...%20if%20you%20want%20to%20fight%2C%20come%20let's%20have%20a%20bout%20(%26quot%3B%3Cem%3Eaao%20do-do%20haath%20kar%20lo%3C%2Fem%3E%26quot%3B).%20This%20rice-daal%20eater%20will%20show%20you%20what%20he's%20capable%20of.%20If%20you%20have%20the%20courage%2C%20launch%20a%20frontal%20attack.%20Stop%20this%20game%20of%20fake%20videos.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsserting%20that%20people%20will%20eventually%20realise%20they%20are%20being%20misguided%20and%20punish%20the%20Congress%20for%20it%2C%20the%20PM%20said%20the%20party%20has%20been%20trying%20to%20say%20that%20the%20BJP%20is%20seeking%20400%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20to%20change%20the%20Constitution%20and%20tinker%20with%20reservation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDon't%20they%20know%20that%20with%20the%20support%20of%20the%20Biju%20Janata%20Dal%20and%20the%20YSR%20Congress%20Party%2C%20who%20were%20not%20part%20of%20the%20NDA%2C%20I%20already%20had%20400%20MPs%20for%20five%20years%3F%20But%20we%20were%20not%20born%20to%20commit%20this%20sin%2C%20nor%20is%20this%20the%20road%20we%20want%20to%20take.%20We%20will%20maintain%20the%20purity%20of%20the%20Constitution%20given%20by%20Babasaheb%20Ambedkar%20and%20the%20other%20framers%20and%20protect%20it.%20Till%20Modi%20is%20alive%2C%20I%20will%20not%20allow%20the%20Congress%20to%20play%20the%20game%20of%20reservation%20based%20on%20religion%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister%20assured%20his%20audience%20that%20the%20reservations%20given%20to%20SCs%2C%20STs%2C%20OBCs%20and%20the%20poor%20among%20the%20general%20category%20were%20given%20based%20on%20the%20Constitution%20and%20that%20nobody%20could%20change%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERepeating%20the%20%26quot%3B%3Cem%3Eshehzade%3C%2Fem%3E%26quot%3B%20(prince)%20jibe%20against%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20PM%20Modi%20said%20the%20Congress%20wanted%20to%20snatch%20reservation%20from%20Dalits%2C%20tribals%2C%20OBCs%20and%20the%20poor%20and%20give%20it%20to%20Muslims%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20religion.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20have%20started%20an%20experiment%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20in%20Karnataka%2C%20they%20want%20to%20take%20away%20reservation%20for%20their%20vote%20bank.%20In%20Karnataka%2C%20they%20declared%20Muslims%20OBCs%20and%20looted%20the%20reservation%20given%20to%20OBCs.%20This%20is%20why%20they%20are%20misleading%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20claimed%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20should%20declare%20that%20they%20will%20not%20give%20reservation%20based%20on%20religion.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%2026%20seats%20in%20Gujarat%20will%20vote%20in%20the%20third%20phase%20on%20May%207.%20Results%20will%20be%20declared%20on%20June%204.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714570980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Ffjeke8oo_pm-modi_625x300_01_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-elections-2024-we-werent-born-to-commit-sin-of-changing-constitution-pm-5565568%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Launching%20an%20acerbic%20attack%20on%20the%20Congress%20on%20his%20home%20turf%20of%20Gujarat%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20has%20said%20the%20party%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bfake%20factory%26quot%3B%20and%20accused%20it%20of%20using%20doctored%20videos%20to%20mislead%20the%20people%20during%20the%20ongoing%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22eng