%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bitcoin%20will%20drop%2013%25%20to%20%2450%2C000%20after%20falling%20below%20a%20key%20support%20level%20as%20macro%20drivers%20slow%2C%20Standard%20Chartered%20says%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Bitcoin%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F663230d910dfcda409653366%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ENamthip%20Muanthongthae%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EBitcoin's%20break%20below%20%2458%2C000%20on%20Wednesday%20clears%20a%20path%20for%20it%20to%20fall%20as%20low%20as%20%2450%2C000%2C%20Standard%20Chartered%20said%20in%20new%20research.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20crypto's%20decline%20has%20been%20driven%20by%20rising%20ETF%20outflows%20and%20falling%20US%20liquidity%20levels.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EBut%20the%20firm%20has%20long%20been%20bullish%20on%20bitcoin%2C%20and%20still%20expects%20the%20token%20to%20reach%20%24150%2C000%20this%20year.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EDeteriorating%20conditions%20are%20denting%20the%20Bitcoin%20rally%2C%20with%20this%20week's%20drop%20below%20%2460%2C000%20putting%20it%20en%20route%20for%20an%20even%20lower%20price%20range.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20commentary%20from%20Standard%20Chartered%2C%20the%20apex%20token%20could%20temporarily%20reach%20as%20low%20as%20%2450%2C000%2C%20signaling%20an%20over%2013%25%20drop%20from%20current%20levels.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20of%209%20a.m.%20ET%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20bitcoin%20is%20trading%20at%20%2457%2C790.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESteering%20this%20decline%20are%20both%20crypto%20and%20macroeconomic%20drivers%2C%20Head%20of%20FX%20Research%20Geoff%20Kendrick%20wrote%20on%20Wednesday.%20Among%20these%20are%20shrinking%20investments%20in%20spot%20bitcoin%20ETFs%2C%20funds%20that%20first%20sparked%20the%20rally%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbitcoin-etfs-approved-by-the-sec-how-to-trade-2024-1%5C%22%3Ethe%20year's%20start%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOn%20the%20crypto-specific%2C%20we%20have%20now%20had%20five%20days%20in%20a%20row%20of%20outflows%20from%20the%20US%20spot%20ETFs%20and%2C%20as%20importantly%2C%20we%20are%20now%20below%20the%20average%20ETF%20purchase%20price%20of%20around%2058k%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThis%20means%20that%20more%20than%20half%20of%20the%20spot%20ETF%20positions%20are%20under%20water%20and%20so%20the%20risk%20of%20liquidation%20of%20some%20of%20them%20must%20be%20considered%20as%20well.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20crypto%20industry%20also%20got%20no%20consolation%20from%20headlines%20in%20Hong%20Kong%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20where%20six%20bitcoin%20and%20ethereum%20spot%20ETFs%20were%20launched.%20Most%20of%20the%20news%20focused%20on%20the%20funds'%20low%20turnover%20volume%2C%20even%20though%20their%20net%20asset%20positions%20were%20promising%2C%20Kendrick%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlso%20wearing%20on%20bitcoin%20are%20the%20US'%20falling%20liquidity%20measures%2C%20which%20have%20rapidly%20declined%20since%20mid-April%2C%20he%20noted.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOf%20course%20liquidity%20matters%20when%20it%20matters%2C%20but%20with%20a%20backdrop%20of%20strong%20US%20inflation%20data%20and%20less%20likelihood%20of%20Fed%20rate%20cuts%20it%20matters%20at%20the%20moment%2C%26quot%3B%20Kendrick%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20not%20to%20say%20that%20Standard%20Chartered%20is%20turning%20sour%20on%20bitcoin%2C%20which%20it%20has%20long%20forecast%20as%20rising%20to%20%24150%2C000%20by%20this%20year's%20end.%20Just%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fcurrencies%2Fbitcoin-price-prediction-btc-halving-outlook-miners-etf-standard-chartered-2024-4%5C%22%3Elast%20week%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Kendrick%20published%20a%20note%20where%20he%20reiterated%20the%20price%20target%2C%20despite%20rising%20macroeconomic%20strains.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdding%20to%20his%20optimism%20was%20bitcoin's%20recent%20halving%20event%2C%20which%20would%20cut%20the%20amount%20of%20produced%20supply%20%E2%80%94%20therefore%20lowering%20how%20much%20ETF%20inflows%20were%20necessary%20to%20keep%20prices%20rising.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20March%2C%20crypto%20enthusiast%20Mike%20Novogratz%20added%20that%20bitcoin%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fcurrencies%2Fbitcoin-price-outlook-floor-crypto-etfs-demand-mike-novogratz-blackrock-2024-3%5C%22%3Eunlikely%20to%20drop%20past%20%2450%2C000%3C%2Fa%3E%20again%2C%20as%20the%20recent%20rally%20is%20driven%20less%20by%20macroeconomic%20factors%2C%20but%20by%20investor%20adoption%20of%20the%20crypto.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20a%20correction%20to%20%2450%2C000%20occurred%2C%20he's%20outlined%20that%20it%20would%20only%20be%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fcurrencies%2Fbitcoin-correction-price-rally-crypto-etf-boomers-leverage-record-novogratz-2024-2%5C%22%3Efollowed%20by%20a%20surge%20higher%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbitcoin-price-crash-outlook-50000-etf-outflows-liquidity-standard-chartered-2024-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714570832000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F663230e610dfcda40965336e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fcurrencies%2Fbitcoin-price-crash-outlook-50000-etf-outflows-liquidity-standard-chartered-2024-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Bitcoin%20has%20fallen%20past%20the%20ETF%20purchase%20price%20of%20around%20%2458%2C000%2C%20putting%20over%20half%20of%20ETF%20positions%20underwater%2C%20Standard%20Chartered%20wrote.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22fdemott%40insider.com%20(Filip%20De%20Mott)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarket