iatimes.com%2Findia%2Fcongress-ka-haath-bjps-shehzad-poonawalla-attacks-rahul-gandhi-over-pakistan-leaders-tweet%2Farticleshow%2F109757942.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20NEWS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fcongress-ka-haath-bjps-shehzad-poonawalla-attacks-rahul-gandhi-over-pakistan-leaders-tweet%2Farticleshow%2F109757942.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Hindu%20Marriage%20Not%20Valid%20Unless%20Performed%20With%20Requisite%20Ceremonies%3A%20Court%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20Hindu%20marriage%20is%20not%20an%20event%20for%20%26quot%3Bsong%20and%20dance%26quot%3B%2C%20%26quot%3Bwining%20and%20dining%26quot%3B%20or%20a%20commercial%20transaction%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20observed%20and%20said%20it%20cannot%20be%20recognised%20in%20the%20%26quot%3Babsence%20of%20a%20valid%20ceremony%26quot%3B%20under%20the%20Hindu%20Marriage%20Act.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20bench%20of%20Justices%20BV%20Nagarathna%20and%20Augustine%20George%20Masih%20said%20a%20Hindu%20marriage%20is%20a%20'samskara'%20and%20a%20sacrament%20which%20has%20to%20be%20accorded%20its%20status%20as%20an%20institution%20of%20great%20value%20in%20Indian%20society.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20recent%20order%20passed%20in%20the%20matter%20of%20two%20trained%20commercial%20pilots%2C%20who%20sought%20a%20divorce%20decree%20without%20performing%20a%20valid%20Hindu%20marriage%20ceremony%2C%20the%20bench%20urged%20young%20men%20and%20women%20to%20%26quot%3Bthink%20deeply%20about%20the%20institution%20of%20marriage%20even%20before%20they%20enter%20upon%20it%20and%20as%20to%20how%20sacred%20the%20said%20institution%20is%2C%20in%20Indian%20society%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20marriage%20is%20not%20an%20event%20for%20'song%20and%20dance'%20and%20'wining%20and%20dining'%20or%20an%20occasion%20to%20demand%20and%20exchange%20dowry%20and%20gifts%20by%20undue%20pressure%20leading%20to%20possible%20initiation%20of%20criminal%20proceedings%20thereafter.%20A%20marriage%20is%20not%20a%20commercial%20transaction.%20It%20is%20a%20solemn%20foundational%20event%20celebrated%20so%20as%20to%20establish%20a%20relationship%20between%20a%20man%20and%20a%20woman%20who%20acquire%20the%20status%20of%20a%20husband%20and%20wife%20for%20an%20evolving%20family%20in%20future%20which%20is%20a%20basic%20unit%20of%20Indian%20society%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bench%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETerming%20the%20marriage%20as%20sacred%20as%20it%20provides%20a%20lifelong%2C%20dignity-affirming%2C%20equal%2C%20consensual%20and%20healthy%20union%20of%20two%20individuals%2C%20the%20bench%20said%20a%20Hindu%20marriage%20facilitates%20procreation%2C%20consolidates%20the%20unit%20of%20family%20and%20solidifies%20the%20spirit%20of%20fraternity%20within%20various%20communities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20deprecate%20the%20practice%20of%20young%20men%20and%20women%20seeking%20to%20acquire%20the%20status%20of%20being%20a%20husband%20and%20a%20wife%20to%20each%20other%20and%20therefore%20purportedly%20being%20married%2C%20in%20the%20absence%20of%20a%20valid%20marriage%20ceremony%20under%20the%20provisions%20of%20the%20(Hindu%20Marriage)%20Act%20such%20as%20in%20the%20instant%20case%20where%20the%20marriage%20between%20the%20parties%20was%20to%20take%20place%20later%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bench%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20April%2019%20order%2C%20the%20bench%20said%20where%20a%20Hindu%20marriage%20is%20not%20performed%20in%20accordance%20with%20the%20applicable%20rites%20or%20ceremonies%20such%20as%20'saptapadi'%20(taking%20seven%20steps%20by%20the%20groom%20and%20the%20bride%20jointly%20before%20the%20sacred%20fire)%2C%20the%20marriage%20will%20not%20be%20construed%20as%20a%20Hindu%20marriage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20further%20observe%20that%20a%20Hindu%20marriage%20is%20a%20sacrament%20and%20has%20a%20sacred%20character.%20In%20the%20context%20of%20saptapadi%20in%20a%20Hindu%20marriage%2C%20according%20to%20Rig%20Veda%2C%20after%20completing%20the%20seventh%20step%20(saptapadi)%20the%20bridegroom%20says%20to%20his%20bride%2C%20'With%20seven%20steps%20we%20have%20become%20friends%20(sakha).%20May%20I%20attain%20to%20friendship%20with%20thee%3B%20may%20I%20not%20be%20separated%20from%20thy%20friendship'.%20A%20wife%20is%20considered%20to%20be%20half%20of%20oneself%20(ardhangini)%20but%20to%20be%20accepted%20with%20an%20identity%20of%20her%20own%20and%20to%20be%20a%20co-equal%20partner%20in%20the%20marriage%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Hindu%20Law%2C%20marriage%20is%20a%20sacrament%20or%20a%20'samskara'%20and%20it%20is%20the%20foundation%20for%20a%20new%20family%2C%20the%20bench%20noted%2C%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThere%20is%20nothing%20like%20a%20%26quot%3Bbetter-half%26quot%3B%20in%20a%20marriage%20but%20the%20spouses%20are%20equal%20halves%20in%20a%20marriage.%26quot%3B%20Observing%20that%20with%20the%20passage%20of%20centuries%20and%20the%20enactment%20of%20the%20Act%2C%20monogamy%20is%20the%20only%20legally%20approved%20form%20of%20relationship%20between%20a%20husband%20and%20a%20wife.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20(Hindu%20Marriage)%20Act%20has%20categorically%20discarded%20polyandry%20and%20polygamy%20and%20all%20other%20such%20types%20of%20relationships.%20The%20intent%20of%20the%20Parliament%20is%20also%20that%20there%20should%20be%20only%20one%20form%20of%20marriage%20having%20varied%20rites%20and%20customs%20and%20rituals%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20said%20after%20the%20Act%20came%20into%20force%20on%20May%2018%2C%201955%2C%20it%20had%20codified%20the%20law%20relating%20to%20marriage%20among%20Hindus%20and%20it%20encompasses%20not%20only%20Hindus%20as%20such%20but%20Lingayats%2C%20Brahmos%2C%20Aryasamajists%2C%20Buddhists%2C%20Jains%20and%20Sikhs%20also%20who%20can%20enter%20into%20a%20valid%20Hindu%20marriage%20coming%20within%20the%20expansive%20connotation%20of%20the%20word%20Hindu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUnless%20the%20parties%20have%20undergone%20such%20ceremony%2C%20there%20would%20be%20no%20Hindu%20marriage%20according%20to%20Section%207%20of%20the%20(Hindu%20Marriage)%20Act%20and%20a%20mere%20issuance%20of%20a%20certificate%20by%20an%20entity%20in%20the%20absence%20of%20the%20requisite%20ceremonies%20having%20been%20performed%2C%20would%20neither%20confirm%20any%20marital%20status%20to%20the%20parties%20nor%20establish%20a%20marriage%20under%20Hindu%20law%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20court%20highlighted%20that%20the%20advantage%20of%20marriage%20registration%20is%20that%20it%20facilitates%20proof%20of%20factum%20of%20wedding%20in%20a%20disputed%20case%20but%20if%20there%20has%20been%20no%20marriage%20in%20accordance%20with%20Section%207%20of%20Hindu%20Marriage%20Act%2C%20%26quot%3Bthe%20registration%20would%20not%20confer%20legitimacy%20to%20the%20marriage%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20noted%20that%20under%20the%20Special%20Marriage%20Act%2C%201954%2C%20a%20man%20and%20a%20woman%20can%20acquire%20the%20status%20of%20being%20a%20husband%20and%20a%20wife%20as%20per%20the%20provisions%20of%20the%20said%20Act.%20%26quot%3BThe%20Special%20Marriage%20Act%2C%201954%20is%20not%20restricted%20to%20Hindus.%20Any%20man%20and%20woman%20irrespective%20of%20their%20race%2C%20caste%20or%20creed%20can%20acquire%20the%20status%20of%20being%20a%20husband%20and%20a%20wife%20under%20the%20provisions%20of%20the%20Special%20Marriage%20Act%2C%201954%20but%20under%20the%20provisions%20of%20the%20Act%20(Hindu%20Marriage%20Act%2C%201955)%2C%20there%20should%20not%20only%20be%20compliance%20of%20the%20conditions%20as%20prescribed%20under%20Section%205%20of%20the%20said%20Act%20but%20also%20the%20couple%20must%20solemnise%20a%20marriage%20in%20accordance%20with%20Section%207%20of%20the%20Act%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExercising%20its%20plenary%20powers%20under%20Article%20142%20of%20the%20Constitution%2C%20the%20top%20court%20declared%20the%20estranged%20couple%20were%20not%20married%20in%20accordance%20with%20the%20law%20and%20held%20the%20marriage%20certificate%20issued%20to%20them%20in%20absence%20of%20valid%20ceremony%20under%20the%20Hindu%20Marriage%20Act%20as%20null%20and%20void.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20quashed%20their%20divorce%20proceedings%20and%20a%20dowry%20case%20lodged%20against%20the%20husband%20and%20his%20family%20members.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714570680000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Ffeclkqj8_hindu-marriage_625x300_08_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhindu-marriage-not-valid-unless-performed-with-requisite-ceremonies-supreme-court-5565179%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20Hindu%20marriage%20is%20not%20an%20event%20for%20%26quot%3Bsong%20and%20dance%26quot%3B%2C%20%26quot%3Bwining%20and%20dining%26quot%3B%20or%20a%20commercial%20transaction%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20observed%20and%20said%20it%20cannot%20be%20recognised%20in%20the%20%26quot%3Babsence%20of%20a%20valid%20ceremony%26quot%3B%20under%20the%20Hindu%20Marriage%20Act.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhindu-marriage-not-valid-unless-performed-with-requisite-ceremonies-supreme-court-5565179%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhindu-marriage-not-valid-unless-performed-with-requisite-ceremonies-supreme-court-5565179%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhindu-marriage-not-valid-unless-performed-with-requisite-ceremonies-supreme-c