ay%2C%20we%20are%20living%20in%20the%20era%20of%20Artificial%20Intelligence.%20As%20we%20have%20seen%20in%20recent%20months%2C%20the%20possibilities%20of%20AI%20are%20limitless%2C%20and%20it%20is%20only%20just%20beginning%20to%20be%20explored.%20People%20across%20the%20world%20are%20now%20using%20the%20powerful%20technology%20to%20help%20them%20accomplish%20a%20variety%20of%20tasks.%20Recently%2C%20a%C2%A0woman%20in%20Bengaluru%20claimed%20that%20her%20date%20used%20AI%20during%20their%20conversation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20post%20on%20Reddit%2C%C2%A0the%20woman%20who%20goes%20by%20the%20name%20%40hustlegurrl%2C%20said%20that%20she%20had%20been%20chatting%20with%20a%20man%20that%20she%20found%20''really%20funny%20and%20was%20super%20entertaining.''%20However%2C%20her%20excitement%20about%20meeting%20him%20in%20person%20fizzled%20out%20when%20she%20realised%20that%20he%20could%20''barely%20speak%20a%20proper%20sentence.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''Was%20looking%20forward%20to%20the%20date%20and%20after%20I%20met%20him%2C%20things%20were%20so%20different.%20He%20could%20barely%20speak%20a%20proper%20sentence.%20Not%20that%20he%20was%20shy%20or%20awkward.%20It%20was%20the%20opposite.%20He%20was%20extremely%20confident%20and%20extroverted.%20But%20all%20that%20language%20and%20wit%20disappeared.%20It%20was%20so%20weird%20I%20was%20a%20bit%20taken%20back%2C''%20she%20wrote.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20their%20conversation%2C%20her%20date%20talked%20about%20AI%20and%20mistakenly%20admitted%20that%20he%C2%A0uses%20AI%20even%20in%20his%20chats.%20That's%20when%20she%20realised%20that%20he%20had%20been%20using%20AI%20to%20impress%20her%20when%20in%20reality%2C%20he%20was%20''dull%20and%20uninteresting.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''We%20drank%20a%20bit%20and%20started%20generally%20talking%20about%20startups%20in%20Bangalore%20and%20AI.%20And%20he%20spoke%20in%20length%20about%20things%20in%20AI%20and%20some%20tools%20he's%20using.%20Then%20he%20let%20it%20slip%20how%20he%20used%20AI%20even%20in%20his%20chats.%20And%20he%20quickly%20changed%20the%20subject.%20That's%20when%20I%20realised%20what%20had%20happened.%20The%20dude%20has%20been%20using%20AI%20in%20all%20his%20chats%20with%20me!!%20And%20in%20person%2C%20he%20was%20dull%20and%20uninteresting.%20I'm%20so%20annoyed%20with%20all%20that%20time%20invested%20it's%20so%20frustrating.%20Seems%20like%20everyone%20in%20Bangalore%20is%20on%20some%20AI%20tool%20and%20I'm%20wondering%20if%20others%20have%20experienced%20this%20too%2C''%20she%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESee%20the%20full%20post%20here%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-embed-height%3D%5C%22316%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reddit.com%2Fr%2Findia%2Fcomments%2F1chbf6a%2Fi_got_aid_on_a_date_in_bangalore%2F%5C%22%3EI%20got%20AI'd%20on%20a%20date%20in%20Bangalore%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cnby%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reddit.com%2Fuser%2Fhustlegurrl%2F%5C%22%3Eu%2Fhustlegurrl%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reddit.com%2Fr%2Findia%2F%5C%22%3Eindia%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20post%20has%20gone%20viral%2C%20generating%20a%20range%20of%20responses.%C2%A0Some%20advised%20her%20to%20talk%C2%A0on%20call%20first%20before%20dates%20to%20avoid%20such%20a%20situation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20user%20wrote%2C%20''The%20best%20you%20can%20do%20to%20avoid%20such%20situations%20is%20to%20talk%20to%20the%20person%20on%20call%20or%20video%20call.%20That%20gives%20some%20idea%20of%20whether%20the%20person%20is%20capable%20of%20holding%20a%20conversation%20or%20not.%20I%20would%20even%20say%20not%20to%20continue%20chatting%20for%20days%20once%20you%20realise%20that%20the%20conversation%20is%20going%20well%20on%20text%20messages.%20Switch%20it%20to%20daily%20voice%20calls%20or%20video%20calls.%20That%20way%2C%20you%20are%20sure%20that%20the%20person%20is%20what%20they%20portrayed%20earlier.%20Voice%2Fvideo%20call%20also%20gives%20a%20room%20for%20spontaneity%20which%20makes%20things%20even%20more%20interesting.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20said%2C%20''That%20sounds%20really%20frustrating%20and%20disappointing.%20It's%20disappointing%20when%20someone%20doesn't%20match%20up%20to%20the%20expectations%20they%20set%20during%20online%20conversations.%20It%20must%20have%20been%20disheartening%20to%20find%20out%20that%20the%20witty%20and%20engaging%20persona%20was%20mostly%20AI-generated.%20''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20third%20said%2C%20''I%20just%20realised%20were%20probably%20soon%20gonna%20have%20people%20get%20catfished%20by%20bots%20and%20taken%20on%20dates%20by%20androids%20posing%20as%20real%20humans.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20fourth%20added%2C%20''This%20is%20so%20funny%20lol.%20Doesn't%20reflect%20well%20on%20the%20guy%20at%20all.%20He%20could%20have%20spent%20his%20time%20on%20character%20AI%20than%20being%20with%20a%20real%20human%20being%20lol.''%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714570020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2F5odesl8_dating_625x300_01_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fbengaluru-woman-claims-her-date-used-ai-to-chat-with-her-was-dull-and-uninteresting-in-person-5565695%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Her%20excitement%20about%20meeting%20him%20in%20person%20fizzled%20out%20when%20she%20realised%20that%20he%20could%20''barely%20speak%20a%20proper%20sentence.''%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fbengaluru-woman-claims-her-date-used-ai-to-chat-with-her-was-dull-and-uninteresting-in-person-5565695%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fbengaluru-woman-claims-her-date-used-ai-to-chat-with-her-was-dull-and-uninteresting-in-person-5565695%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fbengaluru-woman-claims-her-date-used-ai-to-chat-with-