ction%2C%20Katrina%20wrote%2C%20%26quot%3BHappiest%20birthday%20Anushka%20Sharma.%20All%20the%20love%20to%20u%20keep%20shining%2C%26quot%3B%20echoing%20sentiments%20shared%20by%20many%20in%20the%20industry%20and%20among%20fans.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fkatrina-kaif-shares-a-sweet-birthday-message-for-anushka-sharma-keep-shining-all-the-love%2Farticleshow%2F109757192.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20ICC%20Clause%20That%20Can%20Still%20See%20Rinku%20Singh%20Participate%20In%20T20%20World%20Cup%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20Board%20of%20Control%20for%20Cricket%20in%20India%20(BCCI)%20announced%20the%2015-man%20roster%20for%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup%202024%2C%20there%20was%20no%20place%20for%20talented%20stars%20like%20Rinku%20Singh%2C%20KL%20Rahul%2C%20Shreyas%20Iyer%20and%20Ravi%20Bishnoi.%20The%20board%2C%20together%20with%20the%20team%20management%2C%20chose%20a%20mix%20of%20veterans%20and%20IPL%20performers%20as%20it%20named%20the%20squad%20for%20the%20marquee%20event.%20Seeing%20players%20like%20Rinku%20and%20Bishnoi%20miss%20out%20on%20a%20spot%20in%20the%20final%2015%2C%20however%2C%20many%20fans%20and%20pundits%20expressed%20their%20disappointment.%20However%2C%20it's%20not%20all%20over%20for%20players%20like%20Rinku%20yet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20International%20Cricket%20Council%20(ICC)%20had%20set%20May%2001%20deadline%20for%20the%20provisional%20squads%20to%20be%20released%20by%20all%20the%20boards.%20However%2C%20a%20clause%20in%20the%20ICC%20directive%20also%20suggests%20that%20boards%20are%20allowed%20to%20make%20changes%20with%20their%20teams%20by%20May%2025.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20case%20of%20injuries%20or%20other%20issues%20with%20certain%20players%2C%20the%20Indian%20team%20can%20be%20altered%2C%20making%20way%20