%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F663218f3ec0c696569ff74b6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221281%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20stock%20image%20shows%20a%20therapist%20making%20notes%20ahead%20of%20a%20session%20with%20a%20patient.%3Cp%3ETanja%20Ivanova%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EHacker%20Aleksanteri%20'Julius'%20Kivim%C3%A4ki%20was%20sentenced%20to%20over%20six%20years%20in%20prison.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20was%20found%20guilty%20of%20hacking%20a%20therapy%20company%20to%20steal%20notes%20and%20blackmail%20thousands%20of%20patients.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20case%20was%20described%20by%20the%20Finnish%20court%20as%20the%20'largest%20ever'%20in%20the%20Nordic%20country.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Finnish%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcategory%2Fcybersecurity%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehacker%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20been%20sentenced%20to%20six%20years%20and%20three%20months%20in%20prison%20after%20he%20was%20found%20guilty%20of%20stealing%20confidential%20therapy%20notes%20to%20blackmail%20thousands%20of%20patients.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20District%20Court%20of%20Western%20Uusimaa%20announced%20the%20sentencing%20of%20Aleksanteri%20%26quot%3BJulius%26quot%3B%20Kivim%C3%A4ki%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20judges%20found%20the%2026-year-old%20guilty%20of%20all%20counts%2C%20which%20included%209%2C231%20counts%20of%20disseminating%20information%20violating%20personal%20privacy%20and%2020%2C745%20counts%20of%20attempted%20aggravated%20extortion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20charged%20last%20October%2C%20after%20being%20extradited%20from%20France%20to%20Finland.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc97znd00q7mo%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%20BBC%20News%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Kivim%C3%A4ki%20targeted%20around%2033%2C000%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Foikeus.fi%2Fkarajaoikeudet%2Flansi-uudenma