e%20said%20the%20ransom%20would%20increase%20to%20500%20euros%2C%20or%20%24534%2C%20in%20bitcoin%20if%20it%20wasn't%20paid%20within%2024%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20trove%20of%20confidential%20information%20then%20surfaced%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdark-web-tour-2015-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20dark%20web%2C%20%3C%2Fa%3Eincluding%20patients'%20personal%20details%2C%20Social%20Security%20numbers%2C%20and%20sensitive%20therapist%20and%20doctor%20notes%20from%20sessions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20man%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wired.com%2Fstory%2Fvastaamo-psychotherapy-patients-hack-data-breach%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etold%20WIRED%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20information%20discussed%20with%20his%20therapist%20about%20his%20abusive%20parents%20and%20drug%20and%20alcohol%20use%20was%20leaked%20online.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20BBC%20noted%20that%20at%20least%20one%20suicide%20has%20been%20linked%20to%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKivim%C3%A4ki%20denied%20all%20the%20charges%2C%20but%20the%20legal%20bulletin%20cited%20evidence%20presented%20in%20the%20trial%20appearing%20to%20show%20his%20involvement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20he%20had%20used%20a%20pseudonym%20to%20comment%20on%20the%20hacking%20and%20extortion%20in%20an%20online%20message%20board.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20also%20found%20that%20Kivim%C3%A4ki%20had%20used%20a%20server%20implicated%20in%20the%20crimes%20more%20extensively%20than%20he%20had%20admitted%20in%20the%20trial%2C%20and%20used%20an%20encryption%20key%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fwhat-is-my-ip%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIP%20address%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20a%20way%20he%20had%20denied%20in%20his%20testimony.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20also%20cited%20a%20payment%20of%200.1%20bitcoin%20made%20by%20the%20National%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20in%202020%20that%20appeared%20to%20reach%20Kivim%C3%A4ki.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20quality%20of%20the%20crime%20was%20exceptional%2C%20and%20due%20to%20the%20number%20of%20parties%20involved%2C%20it%20was%20the%20largest%20ever%20in%20our%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bulletin%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20proceedings%20have%20yet%20to%20address%20compensation%20claims%20for%20the%20victims.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBrunswick%2C%20an%20international%20public%20relations%20firm%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.brunswickgroup.com%2Fhealthcare-is-disproportionately-susceptible-to-extortion-i22000%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20healthcare%20data%20is%20disproportionally%20susceptible%20to%20extortion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2F30741199%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E2019%20study%20in%20the%20Studies%20in%20Health%20Technology%20and%20Informatics%20journal%3C%2Fa%3E%20outlined%20how%20healthcare%20data%20is%20particularly%20valuable%20to%20cybercriminals%20because%20it%20can%20contain%20financial%20and%20personal%20information%20that%20can%20be%20used%20for%20blackmail%20and%20fraudulent%20purposes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Focrportal.hhs.gov%2Focr%2Fbreach%2Fbreach_report.jsf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edata%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20the%20US%20Department%20of%20Health%20and%20Human%20Services%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bitdefender.co.uk%2Fblog%2Fhotforsecurity%2Fhealthcare-data-breaches-in-us-affect-over-40-million-people-in-2021%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eover%2040%20million%20people%20in%20the%20US%20were%20affected%20by%20healthcare%20data%20breaches%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhacker-stole-therapy-notes-blackmailed-thousands-of-patients-prison-sentence-2024-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A17