nt%20(BJP%20at%20the%20centre%20and%20in%20alliance%20in%20state).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20we%20look%20at%20Maharashtra%20in%20two%20years%2C%20Atal%20Setu%20is%20a%20game-changer%20project.%20Mumbai%20Coastal%20Road%20has%20also%20been%20started%20from%20one%20side.%20We%20gave%20momentum%20to%20many%20projects%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Shinde.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Atal%20Setu%2C%20inaugurated%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20in%20January%2C%20is%20a%2021.8-kilometre-long%20bridge%20that%20connects%20Sewri%20in%20Mumbai%20and%20the%20Nhava%20Sheva%20area%20in%20Raigad%20district.%20The%20Mumbai%20Trans%20Harbour%20Link%20has%20been%20built%20at%20a%20cost%20of%20Rs%2017%2C840%20crore%20and%20is%20the%20longest%20sea%20bridge%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Samruddhi%20Highway%20(Mumbai-Nagpur%20Expressway)%2C%20the%20Metro%20car%20shed%20are%20symbols%20of%20our%20development%20work%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Dharavi%20Redevelopment%20Project%20Pvt%2C%20a%20joint%20venture%20of%20the%20Maharashtra%20government%20and%20the%20Adani%20Group%2C%20is%20the%20biggest%20of%20its%20kind%20in%20Asia%2C%20Mr%20Shinde%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Maharashtra%20government%20last%20year%20approved%20the%20Adani%20Group's%20bid%20to%20redevelop%20the%20area%20that%20covers%20625%20acres%20(253%20hectares)%2C%20and%20has%20been%20described%20by%20officials%20as%20%26quot%3Bthe%20world's%20largest%20urban%20renewal%20scheme%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20project%20is%20a%20key%20step%20in%20reimagining%20one%20of%20the%20largest%20and%20most%20vibrant%20informal%20settlements%20in%20Asia.%20Singapore%20serves%20as%20an%20inspiring%20example%20for%20the%20Dharavi%20Redevelopment%20Project.%20In%20the%201960s%2C%20Singapore's%20landscape%20was%20dotted%20with%20shanties%2C%20slums%20and%20ghettos%2C%20strikingly%20similar%20to%20today's%20Dharavi.%20From%20these%20modest%20beginnings%2C%20the%20Singapore%20Housing%20Development%20Board%20crafted%20over%201.2%20million%20homes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20past%20couple%20of%20years%2C%20the%20state%20government%20has%20also%20started%20a%20steel%20unit%20in%20Gadchiroli%20that%20gave%20employment%20to%2010%2C000%20people%2C%20with%20an%20aim%20to%20reduce%20Maoist%20activities%20in%20the%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20government%20also%20signed%20MoUs%20worth%20Rs%201.36%20lakh%20crore%20at%20WEF%20Davos%20last%20year.%20Removing%20the%20paperwork%20helped%20implement%20these%20MoUs%20at%20lightning%20speed%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20underlined.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714559700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2F941qhbt8_eknath-shinde-ndtv_625x300_01_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Feknath-shinde-on-game-changer-infrastructure-projects-in-maharashtra-5564523%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20steel%20project%20in%20Gadchiroli%2C%20the%20Dharavi%20Redevelopment%20Project%2C%20Atal%20Setu%20are%20some%20of%20the%20infrastructure%20projects%20that%20Maharashtra%20Chief%20Minister%20Eknath%20Shine%20spotlighted%20on%20Monday%20to%20underscore%20his%20government's%20focus%20on%20development.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Feknath-shinde-on-game-changer-infrastructure-projects-in-maharashtra-5564523%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Feknath-shinde-on-game-changer-infrastructure-projects-in-maharashtra-5564523%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Feknath-shinde-on-game-changer-infrastructure-projects-in-maharashtra-5564523%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BCricketing%20Ability%20Over%20Insta%20Likability%26quot%3B%3A%20BCCI%20Slammed%20Over%20Rinku%20Snub%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EKolkata%20Knight%20Riders%20(KKR)%20star%20Rinku%20Singh's%20omission%20from%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup%202024%20squad%20has%20seen%20many%20question%20marks%20being%20raised%20over%20the%20Board%20of%20Control%20for%20Cricket%20in%20India%20(BCCI)%20selection%20committee.%20Rinku%2C%20who%20has%20hardly%20put%20a%20foot%20wrong%20since%20making%20his%20India%20debut%20last%20year%2C%20paid%20the%20price%20of%20the%20Impact%20Substitute%20Rule%20in%20the%20Indian%20Premier%20League.%20Seeing%20Rinku%20being%20overlooked%20for%20the%2015-man%20roster%2C%20former%20India%20cricketer%20Ambati%20Rayudu%20lambasted%20BCCI%20selectors%20over%20the%20decision%2C%20saying%20they%20should%20prefer%20a%20player's%20cricketing%20ability%20over%20another's%20likability%20on%20Instagram.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20scathing%20criticism%20of%20the%20selection%20committee%2C%20Rayudu%20wrote%3A%20%26quot%3BRinku%20Singh's%20omission%20clearly%20indicates%20stats%20rule%20over%20cricketing%20sense..%20who%20in%20this%20selected%20Indian%20has%20been%20walking%20out%20in%20the%2016th%20and%2017th%20over%20in%20a%20t20%20game%20in%20the%20last%202%20years%20and%20playing%20fluently%20with%20a%20high%20strike%20rate%20and%20can%20win%20a%20game%20except%20for%20Ravindra%20Jadeja..%20he%20is%20a%20big%20miss..%20quality%20should%20come%20before%20quantity%20and%20most%20importantly%20cricketing%20ability%20should%20come%20before%20likability%20on%20Instagram.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3ERinku%20Singh's%20omission%20clearly%20indicates%20stats%20rule%20over%20cricketing%20sense..%20who%20in%20this%20selected%20Indian%20has%20been%20walking%20out%20in%20the%2016%20th%20and%2017%20th%20over%20in%20a%20t20%20game%20in%20the%20last%202%20years%20and%20playing%20fluently%20with%20a%20high%20strike%20rate%20and%20can%20win%20a%20game%20except%20Ravindra%20Jadeja..%20he%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20ATR%20(%40RayuduAmbati)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FRayuduAmbati%2Fstatus%2F1785575272060006672%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMay%201%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20not%20part%20of%20the%2015-man%20squad%2C%20Rinku%20was%20included%20as%20a%20reserve%20player%20alongside%20Shubman%20Gill%2C%20Khaleel%20Ahmed%20and%20Avesh%20Khan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERayudu%20isn't%20the%20only%20one%20who%20was%20unimpressed%20with%20Rinku's%20absence.%20Even%20former%20India%20cricketer%20Harbhajan%20Singh%20stated%20that%20Rinku%20should%20have%20been%20included%20in%20the%20squad%20as%20he%20possess%20the%20ability%20to%20change%20the%20complexion%20of%20the%20game%20on%20his%20own.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20feel%20Rinku%20Singh%20should%20have%20been%20included%20in%20the%20team%2C%20a%20player%20who%20has%20the%20potential%20to%20change%20the%20game%20on%20his%20own%20and%20has%20not%20been%20included%20in%20the%20team%20is%20Rinku%2C%26quot%3B%20Harbhajan%20said%20on%20his%20YouTube%20channel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERinku%20made%20his%20Team%20India%20debut%20last%20year%2C%20owing%20to%20an%20exemplary%20IPL%20form.%20He%20struck%20474%20runs%20in%2014%20matches%20at%20an%20impressive%20strike%20rate%20of%20149.53%20and%20at%20a%20batting%20average%20of%2059.25.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20this%20season%2C%20he%20has%20kept%20his%20strike%20rate%20high%20but%20has%20struggled%20to%20muster%20up%20runs.%20In%20nine%20matches%2C%20the%20left-handed%20batter%20has%20scored%20123%20runs%20at%20an%20average%20of%2020.50.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3EWith%20ANI%20inputs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714559700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Ftthjm0h_rinku-singh-bcci_625x300_01_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fipl-2024%2Fcricketing-ability-over-likability-on-instagram-bcci-slammed-ov