3E%3Cp%3EAdventureGenie%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20when%20RVers%20first%20use%20AdventureGenie%20the%20%26quot%3Bjaw-dropping%26quot%3B%20moment%20for%20them%20is%20when%20it%20fills%20in%20the%20blanks%20on%20a%20trip%20with%20stops%20along%20the%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20past%2C%20if%20you%20wanted%20to%20road%20trip%20from%20South%20Carolina%20to%20Yellowstone%2C%20you'd%20have%20to%20look%20at%20a%20map%20and%20try%20to%20plot%20out%20stops%20based%20on%20how%20many%20miles%20a%20day%20you%20want%20to%20drive.%20But%20you'd%20also%20have%20to%20manually%20figure%20out%20whether%20those%20stops%20have%20campsites%20that%20suit%20your%20needs%2C%20or%20if%20they%20have%20any%20other%20attractions%20that%20make%20them%20worth%20passing%20through%2C%20or%20how%20far%20off%20the%20highway%20they%20are.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELengel%20said%20new%20AdventureGenie%20users%20often%20say%20it%20saves%20them%20so%20much%20time%20planning%20their%20trip%20just%20by%20filling%20in%20their%20route.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat's%20pretty%20darn%20rewarding%20for%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EFrom%20Microsoft%20to%20tech%20startup%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELengel%2C%20who%20came%20out%20of%20retirement%20to%20launch%20AdventureGenie%2C%20said%20working%20on%20this%20startup%20has%20been%20a%20major%20change%20of%20pace%20from%20his%20days%20at%20Microsoft%2C%20which%20he%20also%20loved.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20a%20startup%20at%20our%20core%2C%20and%20it's%20a%20lot%20different%20than%20when%20I%20was%20working%20for%20an%20organization%20that%20had%20150%2C000%20employees%20and%20an%20incredible%20budget%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20all%20wear%20lots%20of%20hats%2C%20which%20has%20been%20exciting%2C%20thrilling%2C%20and%20even%20challenging%20from%20time%20to%20time.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20days%2C%20he%20and%20his%20wife%20are%20on%20the%20road%20three%20out%20of%20four%20weeks%20a%20month