u%20water%20them%2C%20the%20wind%20that%20comes%20through%20them%20will%20be%20cooler.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E4.%20You%20can%20also%20use%20terracotta%20coolers%20that%20many%20innovators%20have%20made%20to%20keep%20the%20home%20cool%20as%20they%20are%20more%20sustainable%20in%20nature.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E5.%20One%20important%20principle%20that%20is%20often%20ignored%20in%20practice%20is%20that%20there%20is%20no%20%E2%80%98one-size-fits-all%E2%80%99%20solution.%20%E2%80%9CMost%20regions%20have%20traditional%20techniques%20for%20passive%20cooling%20that%20are%20often%20overlooked%20by%20modern%20architecture%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Ayesha%20Jhunjhunwala%2C%20an%20architect%20and%20director%20of%20Coonoor%20Estates.%20You%20can%20consider%20trying%20out%20traditional%20methods%20to%20cool%20your%20home%2C%20she%20advises.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20in%20hot%2C%20dry%20climates%20such%20as%20Rajasthan%2C%20a%20layer%20of%20inverted%20mud%20pots%20on%20the%20roof%20of%20a%20structure%20can%20significantly%20reduce%20the%20temperature%20of%20the%20building.%20This%20effect%20is%20strongest%20when%20the%20pots%20are%20painted%20white%20to%20increase%20the%20amount%20of%20sunlight%20reflected.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714487577000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F71e1f2ce8e654135b509da9fba6c6619_311592766_142412935197808_3738696823372802622_n-1680175563.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D348728%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22With%20soaring%20temperatures%20and%20warnings%20of%20heatwaves%20in%20several%20Indian%20cities%2C%20architects%20share%20how%20to%20build%20homes%20that%20stay%20naturally%20cool%20and%20don't%20require%20air%20conditioning%20at%20all%20times.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Tina%20Freese%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F348728%2Fheatwaves-imd-warning-architect-tips-keep-home-naturally-cool-air-conditioning-summer-india%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Order%20Organic%20Mangoes%20From%20Farms%20Across%20India%20Using%208%20Online%20Platforms%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EDo%20you%20remember%20rushing%20home%20from%20school%20to%20savour%20a%20bowl%20filled%20with%20fleshy%2C%20yellow%20squares%20of%20delight%3F%20I%20do.%20Summer%20afternoons%20often%20meant%20eyeing%20the%20neighbour%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3Ekairi%3C%2Fem%3E%20(raw%20mango)%20trees%2C%20elated%20when%20the%20green%20beauties%20would%20fall%20to%20the%20ground%20and%20be%20almost%20immediately%20scooped%20into%20our%20baskets.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20summer%20progresses%2C%20no%20Indian%20is%20a%20stranger%20to%20the%20long%20wait%20that%20ensues%20for%20the%20yellowish-green%20hues%20to%20transform%20into%20its%20ripe%20golden-orange%20form.%20And%20no%20one%20questions%20the%20long%20queues%20outside%20popular%20Gujarati%20joints%20whose%20%3Cem%3Eaamras%20puri%3C%2Fem%3E%20(a%20dish%20of%20sweet%20mango%20pulp%20served%20with%20deep-fried%20flatbread)%20is%20%E2%80%9Cto%20die%20for%E2%80%9D%2C%20according%20to%20the%20regulars.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20a%20juicy%20fact%20that%20summers%20in%20India%20are%20incomplete%20without%20mango%20dominating%20our%20homes%20and%20palates.%20This%20comes%20as%20no%20surprise.%20Indians%20have%20been%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F57267%2Fmango-national-fruit-of-india-history%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecultivating%20mangoes%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20thousands%20of%20years%2C%20and%20till%20today%2C%20the%20love%20for%20the%20fruit%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20waned%20even%20one%20bit.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20Alphonso%20continues%20to%20hold%20its%20status%20as%20a%20cult%20favourite%20for%20its%20vibrant%20sweetness%20and%20distinct%20flavour%2C%20there%20are%20hundreds%2C%20if%20not%20thousands%20of%20varieties%20that%20dot%20the%20landscape%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20mango%20cultivation.%20In%20fact%2C%20the%20lesser-known%20varieties%20make%20an%20appearance%20in%20chutneys%2C%20pickles%20and%20the%20like%2C%20lending%20them%20their%20citrusy%20flavour.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20year%2C%20if%20you%20haven%E2%80%99t%20got%20your%20stock%20of%20mangoes%20yet%2C%20here%E2%80%99s%20a%20suggestion%3A%20why%20not%20get%20them%20delivered%20to%20you%20straight%20from%20a%20farm%3F%20We%E2%80%99ve%20put%20together%20a%20list%20of%20people%2C%20startups%20and%20local%20platforms%20that%20are%20bringing%20the%20sweetness%20of%20the%20mango%20from%20the%20tree%20to%20your%20plate.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E1.%20Athalya%20Vandhu%20Ambewale%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCQoWEyejqhU%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCQoWEyejqhU%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%